title: [Girvahk's Shop, Alteration Room]
description: This room is well stocked with all varieties of cloths, trims, and decorative gemstones, all placed on low shelves throughout the rear of the room.  A long, narrow workbench stretches nearly the length of the room, and is covered with a variety of tools for leather working, sewing, woodworking, and metal etching.  Several small kegs under the table contain a variety of metal scraps and thin wires.
